BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:EASTER BUNNY HUNT
DTSTART:20260405T100000
DTEND:20260405T180000
UID:47f370da5b010025@sportsbasement.com
DESCRIPTION:This Easter\, drop by Sports Basement and find some bunnies! I
 f you can write down (or snap a pic of) the locations of all 5 bunnies hid
 ing in your local store\, you'll get 5 easter eggs filled with candy... or
  in some cases\, with Sports Basement gift cards! Candy or gear\, it's all
  good fun. We hope you'll hop on by! We encourage you to bring your eggs b
 ack to us afterwards so we can re-use them next year!
LOCATION:SB Almaden\, SB Presidio\, SB Redwood City\, SB Berkeley\, SB Cam
 pbell\, SB Sunnyvale\, SB San Ramon\, SB Walnut Creek\, SB Bryant St.\, SB
  Stonestown\, SB Novato\, SB Santa Rosa\, SB Orange County\, SB South Bay\
 , SB Long Beach
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/easter-bunny-hunts-at-sports-basement-48
 27694
X-SOURCE:Sports Basement
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:SANTA ROSA RUN CLUB
DTSTART:20260407T180000
DTEND:20260407T190000
UID:e08a16cd404d17f0@sportsbasement.com
DESCRIPTION:Come on out to the Santa Rosa Sports Basement Run Club! This r
 un is all about the fun...lace on up and join us for our weekly run - star
 ting at the store at 9am. It's not just about the miles\; it's about the s
 miles\, the high-fives\, the community vibe\, and sharing our love for Son
 oma County! All levels welcome - hope to see you there! 5k route: https://
 www.strava.com/routes/3283540356429697190
LOCATION:SB Santa Rosa
URL:https://shop.sportsbasement.com/pages/calendar
X-SOURCE:Sports Basement
END:VEVENT
